snippet.title: The Car Care Nut
snippet.description:
Thank you for watching my Channel! My name is AMD aka The Car Care Nut. I am a Toyota Master Diagnostic Technician currently working in the Automotive Industry with over a decade of experience. I have a great passion for cars from Luxury cars to Sport\racing cars. 

Through this channel I'd like to share multiple things. One is my knowledge and experience as a Toyota Master Diagnostic Technician. Also I'd like to share my passion for cars. And while doing all that, throw in a mix of humor and fun. Living up to the saying of "There's no problem big or small that can't be fixed with positive attitude, humor and fun!"

I encourage you to watch the videos, subscribe and leave a comment on one of the videos.

PO Box 2850
Orland Park, IL 60462

Note : If you have questions please leave them as comments on any of the videos. Email questions is difficult at this point. Thank you.
